{
  "chapter": 362,
  "chapter_summary": "本章标题为情敌相逢，分为两条主线。寇仲在洛阳城外与李秀宁短暂告别，两人情感纠葛复杂，李秀宁希望寇仲入关后能再见一面，寇仲则需在入关寻宝与感情之间作出抉择。秦叔宝透露船上仍有王世充眼线，需抓出内奸将计就计。徐子陵扮成岳山独自在桃林客栈歇脚，遭京兆联龙头杨文干设宴拦截，暗处更有杨虚彦和晃公错埋伏。晃公错因祝玉妍之事对岳山怀恨在心，率先出手攻击。徐子陵凭借岳山遗卷的应对之法，以宝瓶印法化解七杀拳劲，随即装遁藏身桌底脱险，成功骗过三名高手。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秀宁是来送行的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柴绍呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不知我来的。唉！你为何不肯见人家呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "见面又能怎样？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为何定要和二皇兄作对，难道不知他真的视你和徐子陵是好朋友吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟也可以阂墙，何况只是萍水相逢的朋友，告诉我，李秀宁究竟是帮你二皇兄，还是李建成、李元吉。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不知道！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公主放心，我今趟入关，对秦王说不定是件好事。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让李靖夫妇陪你们去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个万万不可，因为……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是否要秀宁直接向可汗说才成？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就依公主吩咐吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到长安后，少帅可以见秀宁一面吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这二艘船上的郑兵，是否全在你老哥的控制之下？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_shu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "秦叔宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在还不是，但很快就是啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "将不属我方的人赶下船便成，犯不着杀人，让他们回去传话给子世充，气得他半死更大快人心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_shu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "秦叔宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些事你还是嫩了点儿。我敢立生死状船上必有人通晓王老贼的全盘奸计，且有方法和宋金刚那边暗通消息，只要我们将这人抓起来，施以重刑，撬开他的烂嘴，可将计就计，教宋金刚栽个大筋斗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还是老秦你比我行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_shu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "秦叔宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是否弄上李秀宁那漂亮的妞儿，以至纠缠不清？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这该算是你老哥的疗伤圣药吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李靖和我们的恶嫂子在干甚么呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们的李大嫂并非蛮不讲理的人，只因和我们误会丛生，才不太客气吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我扮岳山到关中找李渊，你却凭甚么鬼方法潜入长安？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只能见机行事，长安的城防这么长，总有破绽空隙，入城后我们再以惯用的手法联络，到时再看看该怎样着手寻宝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我今晚便走，你要小心点。别忘记以李世民的实力，亦要遇袭受创。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有问过李靖关于李小子遇袭受伤的事吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有李大嫂在旁，很多事都不便开口。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天黑后你离船登岸，千万要小心。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也要小心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我会比你迟三天起程，过年前该抵长安，记得算准时间来和我会合。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_wen_gan",
      "speaker_name": "杨文干",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈京兆联杨文干，拜见岳老前辈，特备酒菜一席，为前辈洗尘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎知老夫是岳山？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_wen_gan",
      "speaker_name": "杨文干",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "岳前辈甫再出山，于成都力毙'天君'席应，此事天下谁不晓得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这么曲意奉迎的设宴款待老夫，究竟有何图谋？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_wen_gan",
      "speaker_name": "杨文干",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "岳老火气仍是这么大，何不先坐下喝杯水酒，再容晚辈详细奉告？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "岳山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫正手痒哩！若再浪费老夫的时间，恐要后悔莫及。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_wen_gan",
      "speaker_name": "杨文干",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "岳老是否想入关中呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "岳山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "竟敢来管老夫的事，怕是活得不耐烦了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_wen_gan",
      "speaker_name": "杨文干",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢！只要我给岳老看过一件物品，岳老自会明白一切。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_cuo",
      "speaker_name": "晃公错",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "岳兄果然老而弥坚，只是脑袋仍是食古不化，除非肯答应此生不踏入关中半步，否则明年今日此时就是岳兄的忌辰。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_cuo",
      "speaker_name": "晃公错",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到晃七杀行将入木的年纪，仍看不通瞧不透，甘做别人的走狗，可笑呵可笑！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_cuo",
      "speaker_name": "晃公错",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死到临头竟还口出狂言。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shan",
      "speaker_name": "岳山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我和她的事，那到你来理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_cuo",
      "speaker_name": "晃公错",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "岳霸你以为小妍真的爱上你吗？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_cuo",
      "speaker_name": "晃公错",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走啦！快追！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 362,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    }
  ],
